  The button row is designed to be used within an ``.l-container``.
  It has negative left/right margins to get the buttons aligned
  with the ``fieldset``'s border.

  On mobile the ``button-row__button`` element is a block element
  (100% width).

  There may only be one ``.button-row__button`` and one
  ``.button-row__button.button-row__button--right``.

